_:Ncefc7cfc88cd4cfcbea0729c825a1100 <http://schema.org/description> "British Wool collects, grades, promotes and markets British wool on behalf of sheep farmers from across the UK. Its mission is to increase sustainable demand for British wool in order to maximise returns for members. British Wool works with the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs ." .
